# Angular + Material Project - Project Guidelines

## Project Overview
...Your project short description...

Built with Angular and Angular Material, following Material Design principles and Angular best practices.

## Development Guidelines

### UI/UX Guidelines
- Follow Material Design specifications
- Use Material theming system:
  - Define custom palettes in `_theme.scss`
  - Use proper color variables
  - Implement proper typography scale
- Implement proper responsive design
- Use proper Material density
- Follow accessibility guidelines

### Component Architecture
- Extend Material components properly:
  - Use proper inheritance patterns
  - Implement proper form field controls
  - Use proper overlay strategies
- Implement proper component hierarchy:
  - Layout components
  - Container components
  - Presentational components
- Use Material CDK when needed:
  - Virtual scrolling
  - Drag and drop
  - Overlay
  - Accessibility

### Coding Standards
- Follow Angular Material best practices
- Implement proper theme customization
- Use proper Material typography
- Follow proper form field implementation
- Implement proper dialog patterns
- Use proper Material icons
- Follow proper animation patterns

### Material-Specific Guidelines
- Use proper Material components:
  - Mat-table with proper data source
  - Mat-form-field with proper validation
  - Mat-dialog with proper configuration
  - Mat-snackbar for notifications
  - Mat-menu with proper positioning
- Implement proper Material layouts:
  - Use flex layout properly
  - Implement proper grid system
  - Use proper spacing system

### Development Environment

#### Requirements
- Node.js version: 20.x
- Angular CLI: 17.x
- Angular Material: 17.x
- TypeScript: 5.x

#### Dependencies
Core dependencies:
- Angular 17.x
- Angular Material 17.x
- Angular CDK
- Material Icons
- RxJS 7.x

#### Testing Requirements
- Test Material components properly
- Use Material harnesses
- Implement proper overlay testing
- Test theme switching
- Test accessibility

### Component Guidelines
- Use proper Material mixins
- Implement proper theme switching
- Use proper Material typography
- Follow proper form implementation
- Use proper dialog patterns
- Implement proper table patterns
- Follow proper navigation patterns

### Material Theming
- Define proper color palettes
- Use proper contrast colors
- Implement proper dark theme
- Use proper typography scale
- Follow proper density scale
- Implement proper elevation

### Accessibility Guidelines
- Use proper ARIA labels
- Implement proper focus management
- Use proper color contrast
- Follow proper keyboard navigation
- Implement proper screen reader support

### Performance Guidelines
- Use proper virtual scrolling
- Implement proper lazy loading
- Use proper Material tree-shaking
- Follow proper bundle optimization
- Implement proper caching strategy

### Required Environment Variables
Environment configuration in `src/environments/`:
- environment.ts
- environment.prod.ts
Reference `environment.example.ts` for required variables.

### Additional Material-Specific Tools
- Material Theme Generator
- Material Icons Library
- Material Color Tool
- Material Typography Tool
